<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Questionario completato</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32.png">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="192x192" href="/favicon-192.png">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f0f2f5; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 48px 40px; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08); max-width: 480px; width: 100%; text-align: center; }
    .check { width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 50%; background: #f0fdf4; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 24px; }
    .check svg { width: 32px; height: 32px; color: #16a34a; }
    h1 { font-size: 22px; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    p { font-size: 14px; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .result-box { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .score { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; color: #2c3e50; }
    .score span { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; color: #999; }
    .level { display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; padding: 4px 16px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; }
    .level-Principiante { background: #fef2f2; color: #dc2626; }
    .level-Intermedio { background: #fffbeb; color: #d97706; }
    .level-Avanzato { background: #f0fdf4; color: #16a34a; }
    .company { font-size: 12px; color: #aaa; margin-top: 16px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <img src="/logo.png" alt="Skillcraft" style="width:80px;height:80px;object-fit:contain;display:block;margin:0 auto 16px">
    <div class="check">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h1>Grazie!</h1>
    <p>Il questionario è stato inviato correttamente.<br>Le tue risposte ci aiuteranno a personalizzare il corso.</p>
    <div class="result-box">
      <div class="score"><%= score %> <span>/ 27</span></div>
      <div class="level level-<%= level %>"><%= level %></div>
    </div>
    <div class="company"><%= company.name %></div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
